contexts:
(d) To comply with ¬ß 20-871(b)(3) of the Code, an employer or employment agency must:

(1) Provide information on the employment section of its website in a clear and conspicuous manner about its AEDT data retention policy, the type of data collected for the AEDT, and the source of the data;

(2) Post instructions on the employment section of its website in a clear and conspicuous manner for how to make a written request for such information, and if a written request is received, provide such information within 30 days;
